{"tid":459771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再無將來既連登毒撚","createTime":"2017-11-06T05:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T09:01:31.000Z","uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76fb728964fdbc73fe462b6a736a5b28faa9ec56","tid":459771,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學歷又非專業，多數又係ive仔<br />\n<br />\n畢業人工有15000已經叫好叻<br />\n<br />\n開始返工時都可能有小小熱誠<br />\n<br />\n但你發覺OT無錢比<br />\n<br />\n老細好似你債主咁<br />\n<br />\n吸盡你每一分每一刻工作能力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n有糧出有錢使<br />\n<br />\n但係每月扣晒衣食住行家用又剩幾多？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你好厭倦生活嗎？<br />\n<br />\n仲有排挨<br />\n<br />\n六十五歲先可以退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都未諗退休後有無錢使<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41203f96236697ba8217be7bf9f577a3bea983d6","tid":459771,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:22:47.000Z","msg":"出面返工有老細<br />\n<br />\n屋企又有廢老債主問你攞錢<br />\n<br />\n人生究竟為左乜？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07da292a091fa2069590574f9e8613691b077d62","tid":459771,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:24:56.000Z","msg":"等死"},{"pid":"0a2e84e1dbe1300cd64dc0c296a35cded49a0b37","tid":459771,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死之前有排你挨<br />\n<br />\n日日受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09d7d0e38b8e41e98b67cf86bf7a6707566a690","tid":459771,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死之前有排你挨<br />\n<br />\n日日受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be562bb0e2ab2cc330ae9b926cdd349a466d8d7","tid":459771,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死之前有排你挨<br />\n<br />\n日日受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮人係有錢人養既牛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d48b731d36c9d3a63a73da6b6b6a6f48834b75","tid":459771,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}